@startuml seq_04_manage_profile
title Sequence Diagram: UC-04 Manage Profile

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "User Controller" as Controller
participant "User Service" as Service
participant "Cloudinary" as Cloudinary
participant "User Repository" as Repo

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open Profile / Settings page
User -> Frontend: (2.1) Edit profile information
User -> Frontend: (3.1) Choose avatar or cover image if needed
User -> Frontend: (4.1) Submit profile changes
Frontend -> Controller: (4.2) PUT /api/users/profile (multipart form data)
Controller -> Service: (5.1) Update profile request
Service -> Repo: (5.2) Find user by ID
Repo --> Service: (5.3) User found
Service -> Service: (5.4) Validate profile fields

alt New avatar/cover image uploaded
    Service -> Cloudinary: (8.1) Upload image file
    Cloudinary --> Service: (8.2) Return image URL and public ID
end

Service -> Repo: (6.1/9.1) Update profile information and image metadata
Repo --> Service: (6.2/9.2) Profile updated
Service --> Controller: (10.1) Updated profile data
Controller --> Frontend: (10.2) 200 OK
Frontend --> User: (10.3) Display updated profile
@enduml
